#. <section class="sutta" id="an10.30"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an10.30:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 10"
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "an10.30:0.2"
msgid "3. Mahāvagga"
msgstr ""

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "an10.30:0.3"
msgid "30. Dutiyakosalasutta"
msgstr ""

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "an10.30:1.1"
msgid ""
"Ekaṃ samayaṃ bhagavā sāvatthiyaṃ viharati jetavane anāthapiṇḍikassa ārāme."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an10.30:1.2"
msgid ""
"Tena kho pana samayena rājā pasenadi kosalo uyyodhikā nivatto hoti "
"vijitasaṅgāmo laddhādhippāyo."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an10.30:1.3"
msgid "Atha kho rājā pasenadi kosalo yena ārāmo tena pāyāsi."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an10.30:1.4"
msgid ""
"Yāvatikā yānassa bhūmi, yānena gantvā yānā paccorohitvā pattikova ārāmaṃ "
"pāvisi."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an10.30:1.5"
msgid "Tena kho pana samayena sambahulā bhikkhū abbhokāse caṅkamanti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an10.30:1.6"
msgid ""
"Atha kho rājā pasenadi kosalo yena te bhikkhū tenupasaṅkami; upasaṅkamitvā "
"te bhikkhū etadavoca:"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an10.30:1.7"
msgid "“kahaṃ nu kho, bhante, bhagavā etarahi viharati arahaṃ sammāsambuddho."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an10.30:1.8"
msgid ""
"Dassanakāmā hi mayaṃ, bhante, taṃ bhagavantaṃ arahantaṃ sammāsambuddhan”ti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an10.30:1.9"
msgid ""
"“Eso, mahārāja, vihāro saṃvutadvāro. Tena appasaddo upasaṅkamitvā ataramāno "
"ālindaṃ pavisitvā ukkāsitvā aggaḷaṃ ākoṭehi; vivarissati te bhagavā "
"dvāran”ti."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli5.66"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "an10.30:2.1"
msgid ""
"Atha kho rājā pasenadi kosalo yena so vihāro saṃvutadvāro, tena appasaddo "
"upasaṅkamitvā ataramāno ālindaṃ pavisitvā ukkāsitvā aggaḷaṃ ākoṭesi. Vivari "
"bhagavā dvāraṃ."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an10.30:2.2"
msgid ""
"Atha kho rājā pasenadi kosalo vihāraṃ pavisitvā bhagavato pādesu sirasā "
"nipatitvā bhagavato pādāni mukhena ca paricumbati pāṇīhi ca parisambāhati "
"nāmañca sāveti:"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an10.30:2.3"
msgid "“rājāhaṃ, bhante, pasenadi kosalo;"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an10.30:2.4"
msgid "rājāhaṃ, bhante, pasenadi kosalo”ti."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "an10.30:3.1"
msgid ""
"“Kaṃ pana tvaṃ, mahārāja, atthavasaṃ sampassamāno imasmiṃ sarīre evarūpaṃ "
"paramanipaccakāraṃ karosi, mettūpahāraṃ upadaṃsesī”ti?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an10.30:3.2"
msgid ""
"“Kataññutaṃ kho ahaṃ, bhante, kataveditaṃ sampassamāno bhagavati evarūpaṃ "
"paramanipaccakāraṃ karomi, mettūpahāraṃ upadaṃsemi."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc4"></a>
msgctxt "an10.30:4.1"
msgid ""
"Bhagavā hi, bhante, bahujanahitāya paṭipanno bahujanasukhāya bahuno janassa "
"ariye ñāye patiṭṭhāpitā yadidaṃ kalyāṇadhammatāya kusaladhammatāya."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an10.30:4.2"
msgid ""
"Yampi, bhante, bhagavā bahujanahitāya paṭipanno bahujanasukhāya bahuno "
"janassa ariye ñāye patiṭṭhāpitā yadidaṃ kalyāṇadhammatāya kusaladhammatāya, "
"idampi kho ahaṃ, bhante, atthavasaṃ sampassamāno bhagavati evarūpaṃ "
"paramanipaccakāraṃ karomi, mettūpahāraṃ upadaṃsemi. (1)"
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc5"></a>
msgctxt "an10.30:5.1"
msgid ""
"Puna caparaṃ, bhante, bhagavā sīlavā vuddhasīlo ariyasīlo kusalasīlo "
"kusalasīlena samannāgato."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an10.30:5.2"
msgid ""
"Yampi, bhante, bhagavā sīlavā vuddhasīlo ariyasīlo kusalasīlo kusalasīlena "
"samannāgato, idampi kho ahaṃ, bhante, atthavasaṃ sampassamāno bhagavati "
"evarūpaṃ paramanipaccakāraṃ karomi, mettūpahāraṃ upadaṃsemi. (2)"
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli5.67"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc6"></a>
msgctxt "an10.30:6.1"
msgid ""
"Puna caparaṃ, bhante, bhagavā dīgharattaṃ āraññiko, araññavanapatthāni "
"pantāni senāsanāni paṭisevati."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an10.30:6.2"
msgid ""
"Yampi, bhante, bhagavā dīgharattaṃ āraññiko, araññavanapatthāni pantāni "
"senāsanāni paṭisevati, idampi kho ahaṃ, bhante, atthavasaṃ sampassamāno "
"bhagavati evarūpaṃ paramanipaccakāraṃ karomi, mettūpahāraṃ upadaṃsemi. (3)"
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc7"></a>
msgctxt "an10.30:7.1"
msgid ""
"Puna caparaṃ, bhante, bhagavā santuṭṭho "
"itarītaracīvarapiṇḍapātasenāsanagilānapaccayabhesajjaparikkhārena."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an10.30:7.2"
msgid ""
"Yampi, bhante, bhagavā santuṭṭho "
"itarītaracīvarapiṇḍapātasenāsanagilānapaccayabhesajjaparikkhārena, idampi "
"kho ahaṃ, bhante, atthavasaṃ sampassamāno bhagavati evarūpaṃ "
"paramanipaccakāraṃ karomi, mettūpahāraṃ upadaṃsemi. (4)"
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc8"></a>
msgctxt "an10.30:8.1"
msgid ""
"Puna caparaṃ, bhante, bhagavā āhuneyyo pāhuneyyo dakkhiṇeyyo añjalikaraṇīyo "
"anuttaraṃ puññakkhettaṃ lokassa."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an10.30:8.2"
msgid ""
"Yampi, bhante, bhagavā āhuneyyo pāhuneyyo dakkhiṇeyyo añjalikaraṇīyo "
"anuttaraṃ puññakkhettaṃ lokassa, idampi kho ahaṃ, bhante, atthavasaṃ "
"sampassamāno bhagavati evarūpaṃ paramanipaccakāraṃ karomi, mettūpahāraṃ "
"upadaṃsemi. (5)"
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc9"></a>
msgctxt "an10.30:9.1"
msgid ""
"Puna caparaṃ, bhante, bhagavā yāyaṃ kathā abhisallekhikā "
"cetovivaraṇasappāyā, seyyathidaṃ—appicchakathā santuṭṭhikathā pavivekakathā "
"asaṃsaggakathā vīriyārambhakathā sīlakathā samādhikathā paññākathā "
"vimuttikathā vimuttiñāṇadassanakathā, evarūpāya kathāya nikāmalābhī "
"akicchalābhī akasiralābhī."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an10.30:9.2"
msgid ""
"Yampi, bhante, bhagavā yāyaṃ kathā abhisallekhikā cetovivaraṇasappāyā, "
"seyyathidaṃ—appicchakathā … pe … vimuttiñāṇadassanakathā, evarūpāya kathāya "
"nikāmalābhī akicchalābhī akasiralābhī, idampi kho ahaṃ, bhante, atthavasaṃ "
"sampassamāno bhagavati evarūpaṃ paramanipaccakāraṃ karomi, mettūpahāraṃ "
"upadaṃsemi. (6)"
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli5.68"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc10"></a>
msgctxt "an10.30:10.1"
msgid ""
"Puna caparaṃ, bhante, bhagavā catunnaṃ jhānānaṃ ābhicetasikānaṃ "
"diṭṭhadhammasukhavihārānaṃ nikāmalābhī akicchalābhī akasiralābhī."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an10.30:10.2"
msgid ""
"Yampi, bhante, bhagavā catunnaṃ jhānānaṃ ābhicetasikānaṃ "
"diṭṭhadhammasukhavihārānaṃ nikāmalābhī akicchalābhī akasiralābhī, idampi kho "
"ahaṃ, bhante, atthavasaṃ sampassamāno bhagavati evarūpaṃ paramanipaccakāraṃ "
"karomi, mettūpahāraṃ upadaṃsemi. (7)"
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc11"></a>
msgctxt "an10.30:11.1"
msgid ""
"Puna caparaṃ, bhante, bhagavā anekavihitaṃ pubbenivāsaṃ anussarati, "
"seyyathidaṃ—ekampi jātiṃ dvepi jātiyo tissopi jātiyo catassopi jātiyo "
"pañcapi jātiyo dasapi jātiyo vīsampi jātiyo tiṃsampi jātiyo cattālīsampi "
"jātiyo paññāsampi jātiyo jātisatampi jātisahassampi jātisatasahassampi "
"anekepi saṃvaṭṭakappe anekepi vivaṭṭakappe anekepi saṃvaṭṭavivaṭṭakappe: ‘"
"amutrāsiṃ evaṃnāmo evaṅgotto evaṃvaṇṇo evamāhāro evaṃsukhadukkhappaṭisaṃvedī "
"evamāyupariyanto, so tato cuto amutra udapādiṃ; tatrāpāsiṃ evaṃnāmo "
"evaṅgotto evaṃvaṇṇo evamāhāro evaṃsukhadukkhappaṭisaṃvedī evamāyupariyanto, "
"so tato cuto idhūpapanno’ti. Iti sākāraṃ sauddesaṃ anekavihitaṃ pubbenivāsaṃ "
"anussarati."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an10.30:11.2"
msgid ""
"Yampi, bhante, bhagavā anekavihitaṃ pubbenivāsaṃ anussarati, seyyathidaṃ—"
"ekampi jātiṃ dvepi jātiyo … pe … iti sākāraṃ sauddesaṃ anekavihitaṃ "
"pubbenivāsaṃ anussarati, idampi kho ahaṃ, bhante, atthavasaṃ sampassamāno "
"bhagavati evarūpaṃ paramanipaccakāraṃ karomi, mettūpahāraṃ upadaṃsemi. (8)"
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli5.69"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc12"></a>
msgctxt "an10.30:12.1"
msgid ""
"Puna caparaṃ, bhante, bhagavā dibbena cakkhunā visuddhena "
"atikkantamānusakena satte passati cavamāne upapajjamāne hīne paṇīte suvaṇṇe "
"dubbaṇṇe, sugate duggate yathākammūpage satte pajānāti: ‘ime vata bhonto "
"sattā kāyaduccaritena samannāgatā vacīduccaritena samannāgatā "
"manoduccaritena samannāgatā ariyānaṃ upavādakā micchādiṭṭhikā "
"micchādiṭṭhikammasamādānā, te kāyassa bhedā paraṃ maraṇā apāyaṃ duggatiṃ "
"vinipātaṃ nirayaṃ upapannā; ime vā pana bhonto sattā kāyasucaritena "
"samannāgatā vacīsucaritena samannāgatā manosucaritena samannāgatā ariyānaṃ "
"anupavādakā sammādiṭṭhikā sammādiṭṭhikammasamādānā, te kāyassa bhedā paraṃ "
"maraṇā sugatiṃ saggaṃ lokaṃ upapannā’ti, iti dibbena cakkhunā visuddhena "
"atikkantamānusakena satte passati … pe … yathākammūpage satte pajānāti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an10.30:12.2"
msgid ""
"Yampi, bhante, bhagavā dibbena cakkhunā visuddhena atikkantamānusakena … pe …"
" yathākammūpage satte pajānāti, idampi kho ahaṃ, bhante, atthavasaṃ "
"sampassamāno bhagavati evarūpaṃ paramanipaccakāraṃ karomi, mettūpahāraṃ "
"upadaṃsemi. (9)"
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc13"></a>
msgctxt "an10.30:13.1"
msgid ""
"Puna caparaṃ, bhante, bhagavā āsavānaṃ khayā anāsavaṃ cetovimuttiṃ "
"paññāvimuttiṃ diṭṭheva dhamme sayaṃ abhiññā sacchikatvā upasampajja viharati."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an10.30:13.2"
msgid ""
"Yampi, bhante, bhagavā āsavānaṃ khayā anāsavaṃ cetovimuttiṃ … pe … "
"sacchikatvā upasampajja viharati, idampi kho ahaṃ, bhante, atthavasaṃ "
"sampassamāno bhagavati evarūpaṃ paramanipaccakāraṃ karomi, mettūpahāraṃ "
"upadaṃsemi. (10)"
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc14"></a>
msgctxt "an10.30:14.1"
msgid "Handa ca dāni mayaṃ, bhante, gacchāma."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an10.30:14.2"
msgid "Bahukiccā mayaṃ bahukaraṇīyā”ti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an10.30:14.3"
msgid "“Yassadāni tvaṃ, mahārāja, kālaṃ maññasī”ti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an10.30:14.4"
msgid ""
"Atha kho rājā pasenadi kosalo uṭṭhāyāsanā bhagavantaṃ abhivādetvā "
"padakkhiṇaṃ katvā pakkāmīti."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an10.30:14.5"
msgid "Dasamaṃ."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an10.30:14.6"
msgid "Mahāvaggo tatiyo."
msgstr ""

#. </p><blockquote class="uddanagatha"><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli5.70"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc15"></a>
msgctxt "an10.30:15.1"
msgid "Sīhādhivutti kāyena,"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "an10.30:15.2"
msgid "cundena kasiṇena ca;"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "an10.30:15.3"
msgid "Kāḷī ca dve mahāpañhā,"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "an10.30:15.4"
msgid "kosalehi pare duveti."
msgstr ""
